===One-day International performance===
ODI debut: vs [[Zimbabwe national cricket team|Zimbabwe]], [[Harare]] - [[Nov 28]] [[2004]]<ref name="cricinfo"/>
* Fastest batsman to reach 1000 and 2000 runs.<ref name="fastest to 1000"/><ref name="fastest to 2000"/>
* Fastest century by an England player (69 balls) (v SA, 2005).<ref name="Thompson fastest century"/>

